    Product Description

    UGREEN Micro USB 2.0 OTG Cable 2 Pack

    Are you still bothered by the complicated traditional data transform methods?

    With this OTG cable, just connect your micro usb phone from male micro usb port and add the driver to female usb port, then you can send the files directly on your phone or tablets easily as a host. Allows you to connect devices, like flash drive, card reader ,mouse or a keyboard to your Micro USB OTG capable tablet computer or Smartphone directly at speed up to 480Mbps, controlling your device with a mouse and keyboard. All in one, it offers a convenient way for quick and easy data reading and backup without host.

    Read more

    Specification:

    1. Micro USB 'B' male connector; USB 'A' female connector port

    2. Support High speed data rate up to 480Mbps

    3. Compliant with USB2.0 standard and backward compliant with USB1.1 standard

    4. Cable Rating: Hi-Speed USB 2.0 up to 480 Mbps data transfer rate

    5. Durable PVC construction, and tinned copper to ensure signal performance

    6. Cable length: 4 inch/10cm

    Easily Control with Game Controller

    Great for playing games on your phone/tablet by connecting game controller(PS3/PS4, etc).

    Please make sure one of your deivces with OTG Function.

    Read Photos from Your Camera

    A convenient way to watch movies, view pictures, listen to music and transfer files by connecting a flash driver or camera; expanding storage from a thumb drive, TF card or external hard drive

    Expanding Storage from Flash Drive

    Its good for expanding storage from a thumb drive, TF card or external hard drive; editing files and documents with keyboard and mouse;

    Read more

    Notes:

    1. Before purchasing,please search online to make sure your phone/tablet had OTG function

    2. The host will be power output status when connect OTG cable,also do not support both OTG and charging at the same time

    3. Watch movie from flash drivers directly is not suggested,it would be better to watch movies by copy file to host first

    4. Support flash drivers format:fat16,fat32,exfat,No NTFS!

    5. For first-time user,please connect the cable to your sets first,and then reset the device

    Question:
    Will this work on a Huawei P9 Lite?
    Answer:
    Only if the Huawei P9 Lite supports USB Host. On the GSM Arena page for it (http://www.gsmarena.com/huawei_p9_lite-7983.php), in the "Comms" section, it does not list "USB Host", so that means that the Huawei P9 Lite would not support plugging in other devices into the phone (so this cable would be useless for that phone).
    By Electrobrainleonard on July 7, 2017

        FON
        5.0 out of 5 stars Pefect OTG Cable for the DJI Spark RC and iPhone.
        Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2017
        Color: BlackVerified Purchase
        These OTG Cables are great. Well made and a very good price. I bought these to use with my DJI Spark RC as a direct connection to my iPhone 7 Plus and THEY WORK perfectly. For any DJI Spark users that want to use their RC with a Cable instead of WiFi these are the cables that work, so many others DO NOT! BTW, there is a sequence that must be followed in order for any OTG cable to work with the Spark RC. Here is what I use:

        OGT Cable Set up on Spark Remote
        Make sure youve paired the RC to the Spark via WiFi First. It must be paired or the first time for the OTG Cable setup to work. Turn off WiFi and turn on Airplane Mode

        1) switch on remote (nothing plugged in)
        2) switch on spark
        3) Wait for green light on controller
        4) switch on ipad/iphone
        5)open up DJI Go4 App you will have a grey screen.
        6) plug in lightning cable to ipad/iphone
        7) plug in usb end of lightning into the otg cable
        8) plug otg cable into remote
        9) pad/controller will make a sound to make connection
        10) You'll get the "This accessory may be etc, etc" HIT dismiss
        11) Camera view pops up.

        Now you are ready to go.

        Just Me 123
        5.0 out of 5 stars Great!
        Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2016
        Color: BlackVerified Purchase
        A few weeks ago, I got a wired external keyboard for my daughters tablet. At the time, it didnt occur to me that the plug on the keyboard was a USB plug and there was no port on the tablet for that. I went in search of an adapter, and I decided to buy this Ugreen one (bonus that its a 2 pack)..

        The keyboards USB plug (male) plugs into the female USB port on this adapter. Then the male micro B plug of the adapter plugs right into her tablet. It really is that simple!         The cables came individually wrapped in foil backed zip-lock bags that are thick enough to protect the product when carried in a coat pocket, purse or bag. The actual cable length is 123mm, excluding the USB and micro-USB plugs. The plugs themselves are well finished, smooth and symmetrical, and the fit is firm and positive when plugging into a device.         So far I have tried out the Ugreen OTG cables with a video boroscope, 32-1 USB media card reader, and a variety of USB flash drives including HP brand, which are notoriously fickle, and had no problems accessing files via my Moto phone. With an appropriate app from the Play Store, I was even able to plug in my full sized Nikon D700 SLR into my G5 Plus and control it, firing the shutter, changing the settings and getting a live view of what the camera sees via this OTG cable and a USB to micro-USB extension. I'm so pleased and excited by all the new versatility my phone has, and also that I have both a primary and backup cable for what I consider to be a modest price.
